inclusion.criterion: Total serum PSA of 2.0-10 ng/ml at entry and/or suspicious digital rectal examination
inclusion.label: met

exclusion.criterion: Previous prostate biopsy or prostatic surgery
exclusion.label: not_met

exclusion.label: unknown
